text: Anantnag () is a district in the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir in northwestern India. It is one of six districts which make up the Kashmir Valley. The district headquarters is Anantnag. ==Tehsils== *Kokernag Tehsil *Shangus Tehsil *Anantnag Tehsil *Bijbehara Tehsil *Doru Tehsil *Pahalgam Tehsil *Qazigund Tehsil *Kulgam Tehsil Category:Districts of Jammu and Kashmir
